    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>In newer versions of IntelliJ it's under <strong>Code -&gt; Analyze Code -&gt; Run Inspection by Name</strong>.</p>\n<p>In IntelliJ versions before that, you should run it from <strong>Analyze -&gt; Run Inspection By Name</strong>:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/ngUH5m.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/ngUH5m.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n<p>Than, pick <strong>Unused declaration</strong>:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/DGDd6m.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/DGDd6m.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n<p>And finally, <strong>uncheck</strong> the <strong>Include test sources</strong>:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/1Ls86m.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/1Ls86m.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 543178,
      "reputation" : 14013,
      "user_id" : 912236,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/6c7c3dee9495a0251a11b4496ae811a6?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
      "display_name" : "Orwellophile",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/912236/orwellophile"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 4,
    "last_activity_date" : 1601536422,
    "creation_date" : 1601536422,
    "answer_id" : 64150664,
    "question_id" : 6587729,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>After you've run the Inspect by Name, select all the locations, and make use of the <em>Apply quick fixes to all the problems</em> drop-down, and use either (or both) of <em>Delete unused parameter(s)</em> and <em>Safe Delete</em>.</p>\n<p>Don't forget to hit <em>Do Refactor</em> afterwards.</p>\n<p>Then you'll need to run another analysis, as the refactored code will no doubt reveal more unused declarations.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/QmUrH.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/QmUrH.png\" alt=\"Apply quick fixes to all the problems\" /></a></p>\n"
  }, {
