    "body" : "<p>A picture is worth a thousand words! <em>IntelliJ IDEA 2022.x.x</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Go to the <strong>code tab, analyze code</strong>,  and <strong>run inspection by name</strong>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/TDln4.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/TDln4.png\" alt=\"navigation\" /></a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Select what you need</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/3Kkb6.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/3Kkb6.png\" alt=\"settings\" /></a></p>\n"
